{"id":219935,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/轻点鼠标即可危害国家安全/","date":"2012-04-09T13:37:32Z","modified":"2012-04-09T13:37:32Z","title":"轻点鼠标即可危害国家安全","content":"<p>自3月30日中国查处一批传播谣言的互联网站，逮捕6名传播“谣言”的网民以来，官方媒体一直在不断加大批判网络谣言的力度。 昨天CCTV的新闻联播再一次重申网络谣言的危害。在新闻中，法律专家表示，“恶意造谣严重扰乱社会秩序、影响社会稳定、危害社会诚信，应依法受到惩处。”新闻最后评论说，“一些人只需轻点鼠标就诋毁他人名誉，破坏稳定，甚至危及国家安全。”<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1e35b2a2/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&#038;title=%E8%BD%BB%E7%82%B9%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F04%2F09%2F0541214%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E8%BD%BB%E7%82%B9%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F04%2F09%2F0541214%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/04/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/131173299029/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1e35b2a2/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/131173299029/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1e35b2a2/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/131173299029/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1e35b2a2/a2t.img\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=zssetO3JHb8:3C3UIdldjSM:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=zssetO3JHb8:3C3U